Body: .text __start:  add     sum, sum, n next:     add     n, n, 2           # keep n even rem     k, n, 3 beqz    k, next           # skip multiples of 3 ble     n, 72, __start puts    msg put     sum putc    '\n" done (5, ver 2) (10 points) Write a complete SAL program that will add all of the odd numbers from 9 to 105 except for multiples of 5.
